      <title>贸易战期间中国通过每日汇率维持人民币支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/china-maintains-yuan-support-via-daily-fixing-amid-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中美贸易紧张局势不断升级，加大了人民币贬值压力，中国将人民币每日参考汇率设定在7.2以上的水平，加大了对人民币的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/china-maintains-yuan-support-via-daily-fixing-amid-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:22:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度新任储备银行行长改变了交易员的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/new-reserve-bank-of-india-governor-shakes-up-traders-playbook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙克提坎塔·达斯担任印度央行行长最后两年，卢比汇率坚挺，流动性减少，利率居高不下。桑杰·马洛特拉似乎将打破这一模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/new-reserve-bank-of-india-governor-shakes-up-traders-playbook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citadel 正在招聘前摩根士丹利日本商品主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/citadel-is-hiring-ex-morgan-stanley-japan-commodities-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为其在该国电力市场的最新扩张计划的一部分，Citadel 正在聘请摩根士丹利三菱日联证券公司日本大宗商品销售前主管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/citadel-is-hiring-ex-morgan-stanley-japan-commodities-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美贸易战刺激避险需求，黄金创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-trade-war-stokes-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中美贸易战的爆发刺激了避险需求，金价在上一交易日上涨近 1% 后，升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-trade-war-stokes-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 00:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛重新聘用乔瓦尼从事 TMT 交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/goldman-sachs-rehires-giovanni-after-instacart-for-tmt-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社看到的一份内部备忘录显示，高盛集团前银行家尼克·乔瓦尼将重新加入该投资银行，担任他曾经领导的技术、媒体和电信集团的合伙人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/goldman-sachs-rehires-giovanni-after-instacart-for-tmt-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 00:02:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易战担忧与伊朗施压叠加 油价企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对美国和中国之间的贸易战将损害全球经济增长的担忧被唐纳德·特朗普总统加大对伊朗的经济压力所抵消，油价趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 23:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
